                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <div class="padding modalPadding">
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
                                            <p class="lead">At the start screen press
                                                <i>Start</i> to start the game.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> You may also toggle the game's sound by clicking the speaker symbol at the
                                                top right corner</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
                                            <img src="image/img_main/game2_instruct1.png">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="padding modalPadding">
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
                                            <img src="image/img_main/game2_instruct2.png">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
                                            <p class="lead"> The Game will begin with food items falling into the player's cart.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> Each food item belongs to one of the four food groups </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="padding modalPadding">
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
                                            <p class="lead">Each level will give the player a
                                                <i>Shopping List</i> at the bottom right corner.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> The shopping list will indicate the quantity what food items the player
                                                needs to keep in the cart.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> The numerator of each food item indicates the
                                                <b>current </b>quantity of that food item in your cart and the denominator indicates
                                                the
                                                <b>required</b> quantity needed to stay in the cart.</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
                                            <img src="image/img_main/game2_instruct3.png">
                                        </div>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="padding modalPadding">
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
                                            <img src="image/img_main/game2_instruct4.png">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 text-center align-self-center">
                                            <p class="lead"> The player must sort the items of the cart by following what the Shopping List
                                                requires.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> In order to advance to the next level, the player must drag and drop the
                                                uneeded items from the cart to the shelves accordingly. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="padding modalPadding">
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
