                                                <br>
                                                <br> If the timer runs out, the player loses.
                                                <br>
                                                <br> Players can also lose if too much food is returned to the shelves, as the
                                                player may not be able to meet the requirement of the shopping list.
                                                <br>
                                                <br>

                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
